            .block {

                display: block;
                margin: auto;
            }

              font-style: normal;
            }

            @font-face {

              src: url("http://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0029/8962/t/8/assets/univers-condensedlight-webfont.eot");
              src: local("?????????"), url(data:font/truetype;charset=utf-8;base64,) format("truetype"), url("univers-condensedlight-webfont.svg#webfont6HRVh9gN") format("svg");
              font-weight: normal;
              font-style: normal;
            }
            .header {
            }

            .header .centered {
                /* generated from http://www.colorzilla.com/gradient-editor/ */
                background: black; /* Old browsers */
                background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, rgba(114,114,114,1) 0%, rgba(68,68,68,1) 10%, rgba(0,0,0,1) 45%, rgba(0,0,0,1) 100%); /* FF3.6+ */
                background: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0%,rgba(114,114,114,1)), color-stop(10%,rgba(68,68,68,1)), color-stop(45%,rgba(0,0,0,1)), color-stop(100%,rgba(0,0,0,1))); /* Chrome,Safari4+ */
                background: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, rgba(114,114,114,1) 0%,rgba(68,68,68,1) 10%,rgba(0,0,0,1) 45%,rgba(0,0,0,1) 100%); /* Chrome10+,Safari5.1+ */
                background: -o-linear-gradient(top, rgba(114,114,114,1) 0%,rgba(68,68,68,1) 10%,rgba(0,0,0,1) 45%,rgba(0,0,0,1) 100%); /* Opera 11.10+ */
                background: -ms-linear-gradient(top, rgba(114,114,114,1) 0%,rgba(68,68,68,1) 10%,rgba(0,0,0,1) 45%,rgba(0,0,0,1) 100%); /* IE10+ */
                background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(114,114,114,1) 0%,rgba(68,68,68,1) 10%,rgba(0,0,0,1) 45%,rgba(0,0,0,1) 100%); /* W3C */
                filter: progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.gradient( startColorstr='#727272', endColorstr='#000000',GradientType=0 ); /* IE6-9 */
                width: 960px;
                margin: auto;
                padding: 0px 7px;
                -webkit-border-radius: 4px;
                -moz-border-radius: 4px;
                border-radius: 4px;
            }


            .header .centered > img {
                margin-left: 10px;
            }

            .header ul {
                display: inline;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                padding-top: 12px;
                font-family: "Univers47CondensedLight", "Arial Narrow", Helvetica, sans-serif;
                font-size: 14px;
                font-style: normal;
                font-variant: normal;
                font-weight: normal;
                white-space: nowrap;
            }

            .header .centered > ul {
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

            .header li {
                list-style-type: none;
            }

            .header .centered > ul > li {
                display: inline-block;
                position: relative;
                padding: 7px 10px;
            }

            .header .centered a {
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .header .centered > ul > li > a {
                color: white;
            }

            .header .centered > ul > li:hover > a {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

            .header .centered > ul > li .hover-menu {
                position: absolute;
                display: none;
                padding-top:10px;
            }

            .header .centered .inner {
                min-width: 140px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                background: white;
                border: 5px solid black;
                padding-bottom: 10px;
                display: block;
                position: relative;
                z-index: 10;

                -webkit-border-radius: 8px;
                -moz-border-radius: 8px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }


            .header .centered .inner li {
                padding: 5px 0;
                padding-left: 15px;
                padding-right: 4px;
            }

            .header .centered .inner li a {
                color: black;
            }

            .header .centered .inner li:hover a {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

            .featured.product .logo {
                width: 100px;
                height: auto;
                margin-right: 50px;
                float: left;
            }

            .featured.product .logo img {
                max-height: 400px;
            }

            .featured.product .wrapper {
                overflow: hidden;
                width: 800px;
            }

            .featured.product .table {
                display: table;
                table-layout: fixed;
                width: 800px;
                margin-top: 10px;
            }

            .featured.product .image-div {
                width: 400px;
                display: table-cell;
                vertical-align:middle;
            }

            .featured.product .image {
                max-width: 400px;
                max-height: 300px;
                width: auto;
                height: auto;
                display: block;
                margin: auto;

                -webkit-box-shadow: 4px 4px 20px rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.35);
                -moz-box-shadow:    4px 4px 20px rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.35);
                box-shadow:         4px 4px 20px rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.35);
            }

            .featured.product .info {
                max-width: 400px;
                width: auto;
                margin-left: 20px;
            }

            .featured.product .info > * {
                margin: 20px;
            }

            .featured.product .buy-div {
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            .featured.product .title {
                text-align: right;
                margin: 20px;
                font-family: Arial;
                font-size: 41px;
                color: black;
            }

            .featured.product .price {
                font-family: Arial;
                font-size: 22px;
                color: #666;
            }


            .featured.product .description {
                font-family: Arial;
            }

            .buy {
                padding: 15px 40px;
                -webkit-border-radius: 4px;
                -moz-border-radius: 4px;
                border-radius: 4px;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                font-size: 15px;
                color: #FFF;

                /* generated with http://www.colorzilla.com/gradient-editor/ */
                background: rgb(219,4,7); /* Old browsers */
                background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, rgba(219,4,7,1) 0%, rgba(142,0,2,1) 100%); /* FF3.6+ */
                background: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0%,rgba(219,4,7,1)), color-stop(100%,rgba(142,0,2,1))); /* Chrome,Safari4+ */
                background: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, rgba(219,4,7,1) 0%,rgba(142,0,2,1) 100%); /* Chrome10+,Safari5.1+ */
                background: -o-linear-gradient(top, rgba(219,4,7,1) 0%,rgba(142,0,2,1) 100%); /* Opera 11.10+ */
                background: -ms-linear-gradient(top, rgba(219,4,7,1) 0%,rgba(142,0,2,1) 100%); /* IE10+ */
                background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(219,4,7,1) 0%,rgba(142,0,2,1) 100%); /* W3C */
                filter: progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.gradient( startColorstr='#db0407', endColorstr='#8e0002',GradientType=0 ); /* IE6-9 */
            }

            .featured.product .twitter.button {
                overflow:hidden;
            }

            .featured.product .text {
                text-align:left;
            }

            .featured.product .spacer {
                clear: both;
            }

            .divider {
                padding: 40px 0px;
                position: relative;
                clear: both;
                height: 1px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .divider .bar {
                height: 1px;

                /* Old browsers */
                background: #ffffff;

                /* FF3.6+ */
                background: -moz-linear-gradient(left,  #ffffff 0%, #d5d5d5 25%, #d5d5d5 75%, #ffffff 100%);

                /* Chrome,Safari4+ */
                background: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, right top, color-stop(0%,#ffffff), color-stop(25%,#d5d5d5), color-stop(75%,#d5d5d5), color-stop(100%,#ffffff));

                /* Chrome10+,Safari5.1+ */
                background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left,  #ffffff 0%,#d5d5d5 25%,#d5d5d5 75%,#ffffff 100%);

                /* Opera 11.10+ */
                background: -o-linear-gradient(left,  #ffffff 0%,#d5d5d5 25%,#d5d5d5 75%,#ffffff 100%);

                /* IE10+ */
                background: -ms-linear-gradient(left,  #ffffff 0%,#d5d5d5 25%,#d5d5d5 75%,#ffffff 100%);

                /* W3C */
                background: linear-gradient(left,  #ffffff 0%,#d5d5d5 25%,#d5d5d5 75%,#ffffff 100%);

                /* IE6-9 */
                filter: progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.gradient( startColorstr='#ffffff', endColorstr='#ffffff',GradientType=1 );
            }

            .divider .text {
                color: #848484;
                font-size: 14px;
                position: relative ;
                top: -8px;
                padding-left: 20px;
                padding-right: 20px;
                background: #fff;
                -moz-box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 10px #fff;
                -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 10px #fff;
                -o-box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 10px #fff;
                box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 10px #fff;
            }

            .block {
                /* generated using http://css3gen.com/box-shadow/ */
                -webkit-box-shadow: 4px 4px 20px rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.35);
                -moz-box-shadow:    4px 4px 20px rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.35);
                box-shadow:         4px 4px 20px rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.35);
            }

            .block.product {
                margin: 50px 15px;
            }

            .block.product .title {
                position: absolute;
                font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                font-size: 13px;
                color: white;
                background: rgb(0, 0, 0);
                background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
                filter: alpha(opacity=153);
                -ms-filter:"progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.Alpha(Opacity=153)";
                bottom: 5px;
                padding: 6px 6px;
            }

            .block.product .social {
                position: absolute;
                top: -10px;
                right: -8px;
                width: 176px;
                margin: auto;
                height:25px;
            }

            .block.product .social-buttons {
                position:absolute;
                background: rgb(0, 0, 0);
                background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
                filter: alpha(opacity=153);
                -ms-filter:"progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.Alpha(Opacity=153)";
                padding: 6px 6px;
                padding-right: 0px;
                top: 18px;
            }

            .preview.product .content {
                border: 1px solid #CECECE;

                -moz-box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 2px #CECECE;
                -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 2px #CECECE;
                -o-box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 2px #CECECE;
                box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 2px #CECECE;
            }

            .preview.product .content .image img {
                max-width: 700px;
                max-height: 400px;
                width: auto;
                height: auto;
                display: block;
                margin: auto;
            }

            .preview.product .content .table {
                width: 700px;
                height: 400px;
                display: table;
                table-layout: fixed;
            }

            .preview.product .content .image {
                display: table-cell;
                vertical-align: middle;
            }

            .preview.product .content .title {
                text-align: right;
                font-family: Arial;
                font-size: 41px;
                color: black;
            }

            .preview.product .content .price {
                font-family: Arial;
                font-size: 22px;
                color: #666;
            }

            .preview.product .content .description {
                font-family: Arial;
                max-width: 600px;
                width: auto;
            }

            .preview.product .content .social-buttons {
                float: right;
                margin-top: 180px;
                width: 90px;
            }

            .preview.product .content .social-buttons .button {
                margin: 5px 0px;
            }

            .preview.product .content .social-buttons .facebook.button {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .preview.product .content .text {
                text-align:left;
            }

            .preview.product .content .buy-div {
                float:right;
                margin-right: 10px;
            }

            .preview .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .preview .close {
                color: #BBB;
                font-size: 25px;
                font-family: Arial;
                float: none;
                position: absolute;
                right: 20px;
            }

            .preview .close:hover {
                color: #666;
            }
        </style>
